oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Fan Fair (1997)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Country Music Association (U.S.); Fan Fair; Grand Ole Opry (Radio program); Logos (Symbols); Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing the 1997 International Country Music Fan Fair, presented by CMA and the Grand Ole Opry, in Nashville from June 16 to 21. Poster features a metal photoplate of the Fan Fair logo.
